h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
This is the landing page of *Agent* with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click *Agent* sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Agent* link.
* Show Landing Page of *Agent*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show Agent Company" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Show blank input form on top to [Create new "Agent"|guide:CreateExhAgentActionService].
* [List "Agent"|guide:ListExhAgentActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show *Agent* information in grid view.
** Reset input form on top to create new *Agent*.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

